<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd"><html>
<head>
<title>HIDE-MY-NETWORK</title>
</head>
<body>
<h3><i>This makes my semantic network invisible.</i></h3>
<h3><font size="2" color="gray">Begin micro-behaviour</font>
</h3>
<p><b>HIDE-MY-NETWORK</b></p>
<p><font size="2" color="gray">Begin NetLogo code:</font> </p>
<pre>set my-network-visibility false
ask turtle-set all-nodes-reachable-from my-list-of-anchor-points
    [set my-visibility false
     set hidden? true]
ask link-set all-links-reachable-from my-list-of-anchor-points
    [set hidden? true]</pre>
<font size="2" color="gray">End NetLogo code</font> 
<h2>Related Micro-behaviours</h2>
<p><a href="SHOW-MY-NETWORK.html">SHOW-MY-NETWORK</a> displays my network.
<a href="HIDE-MY-NETWORK.html">HIDE-MY-NETWORK</a> hides it.
<a href="TOGGLE-VISIBILITY-OF-NETWORK.html">TOGGLE-VISIBILITY-OF-NETWORK</a> 
switches its visibility. <a href="HIDE-ALL-NETWORKS.html">HIDE-ALL-NETWORKS</a> 
hides all nodes and links.</p>
